script.name: csv.hacking.watch
script.sourceplaintext:
$last.in.range = [FALSE] $sent.tip = [FALSE] while get global variable: name='csv.hacking.status' @ = wait 100 ms
set global variable: name='csv.hacking.inrange' value=null
skip if $obj.cafe -> exists break
if [PLAYERSHIP] -> is in same sector as $obj.cafe if [PLAYERSHIP] -> has same environment as $obj.cafe
$status = get global variable: name='csv.hacking.status' if $status == 1 OR $status == 4 OR $status == 6 $dist = get distance between $obj.cafe and [PLAYERSHIP]
$in.range = [FALSE] do if $dist >= 20000 AND $dist <= 25000 $in.range = [TRUE]
if $status == 1 $text = 'Code Breaking' else if $status == 4 $text = 'Hacking Core' else if $status == 6 $text = 'Enter Password' end
if $in.range if not $sent.tip $sent.tip = [TRUE] $read.text = read text: page=3895 id=660009 display game tip: text=$read.text delay=8000 end set global variable: name='csv.hacking.inrange' value=[TRUE] $text = sprintf: pageid=3212 textid=10906, $text, null, null, null, null $pos.text = sprintf: pageid=3212 textid=10906, '|', null, null, null, null else $text = sprintf: pageid=3212 textid=10908, $text, null, null, null, null $pos.text = sprintf: pageid=3212 textid=10908, '|', null, null, null, null end $text = $text + ' : '
$dist.tick = $dist / 500 $tick = 0 while $tick < 90 do if $tick == 40 $text = $text + '>' do if $tick == 50 $text = $text + '<'
if $dist.tick == $tick $text = $text + $pos.text else $text = $text + ' ' end inc $tick = end
do if $dist.tick >= 90 $text = $text + $pos.text
display subtitle text: text=$text duration=200 ms if $last.in.range AND ! $in.range START speak text: page=[Page.MiscVoice] id=36 priority=20 else if ! $last.in.range AND $in.range START speak text: page=[Page.MiscVoice] id=1307 priority=20 end $last.in.range = $in.range
else if $status == 3 $read.text = read text: page=3212 id=10921 display subtitle text: text=$read.text duration=5000 ms @ = wait 6000 ms set global variable: name='csv.hacking.status' value=4 $last.in.range = [FALSE] else if $status == 5 $datatype = datatype[ $obj.cafe ] do if $datatype != DATATYPE_SHIP $obj.cafe = change datatype[$obj.cafe] to DATATYPE_SHIP if $obj.cafe -> get local variable: name='csv.sudoku.solved' $read.text = read text: page=3212 id=10913 display subtitle text: text=$read.text duration=5000 ms $read.text = read text: page=3895 id=660006 send incoming message $read.text to player: type:[Log.Important], display it=[FALSE], log it=[TRUE] @ = wait 8000 ms set global variable: name='csv.hacking.status' value=6 $last.in.range = [FALSE] else if not $obj.cafe -> is script csv.sudoku.changevalue on stack of task=144 set global variable: name='csv.hacking.status' value=4 @ = wait 500 ms end else if $status == 7 $read.text = read text: page=3895 id=660008 display subtitle text: text=$read.text duration=200 ms @ = wait 100 ms else if $status == 8 $read.text = read text: page=3212 id=10918 display subtitle text: text=$read.text duration=5000 ms @ = wait 5000 ms set global variable: name='csv.hacking.status' value=6 else if $status == 9 $read.text = read text: page=3212 id=10917 display subtitle text: text=$read.text duration=3000 ms @ = wait 2800 ms set global variable: name='csv.hacking.status' value=10 else if $status == 10 remove object context entry: id='csv.hack' set global variable: name='csv.hacking.status' value=null @ = wait 500 ms send script event: name='csv.hacking.done', object=$obj.cafe, param1=null, param2=null break end end end end return null
